Friends in Vancouver, are you ready to try Toronto’s most famous bubble tea brand, Real Fruit Bubble Tea?

Good news! Real Fruit Bubble Tea, Toronto’s most popular, has arrived in Vancouver, with its flagship store officially opening at Richmond Centre on December 15th.

Founded in 2002 in Toronto, Real Fruit Bubble Tea has expanded with over 120 direct stores in Ontario, Quebec, Vancouver, and multiple states in the United States. Richmond Centre marks the first store in British Columbia for Real Fruit Bubble Tea.

For over 20 years, as a Canadian homegrown brand, Real Fruit Bubble Tea has been beloved by local customers. Beyond milk tea, they offer over 50 handmade drinks, including freshly squeezed juices, smoothies, crush, coffee, and sherbet. All fruits are freshly cut in-store, and each tea is brewed with carefully selected tea leaves. Fresh and authentic, each sip allows you to savor the natural flavors. Different fruits can be mixed and matched, providing consumers with rich and exclusive beverages.

The Mango Diamond Slush is particularly popular, featuring globally selected mangoes, freshly cut mango chunks, and a refreshing and smooth texture that is irresistible. The employees have a “superpower” for selecting the perfect mango with just a touch. Real Fruit Bubble Tea Canada uses over 50 million mangoes annually!

To let friends in Vancouver experience the natural and unique taste, Real Fruit Bubble Tea will have a Buy-One-Get-One-Free promotion on December 21st and 22nd, Thursday and Friday, from 2:30 PM to 5:30 PM. You will get to taste their most popular Mango Diamond Slush.

With countless bubble tea options in Vancouver, what makes this Toronto brand stand out? How fresh can it be? Visit the Food Court on the second floor of Richmond Centre to find out.
